  (function () {
    var noop = function noop() {};
    if ("performance" in window === false) {
      window.performance = {};
    }
    window.performance.mark = performance.mark || noop;
    window.performance.measure = performance.measure || noop;
    if ("now" in window.performance === false) {
      var nowOffset = Date.now();
      if (performance.timing && performance.timing.navigationStart) {
        nowOffset = performance.timing.navigationStart;
      }
      window.performance.now = function now() {
        return Date.now() - nowOffset;
      };
    }
  })();

<script id="wix-first-paint">
    if (window.ResizeObserver &&
        (!window.PerformanceObserver || !PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes || PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes.indexOf('paint') === -1)) {
        new ResizeObserver(function (entries, observer) {
            entries.some(function (entry) {
                var contentRect = entry.contentRect;
                if (contentRect.width > 0 && contentRect.height > 0) {
                    requestAnimationFrame(function (now) {
                        window.wixFirstPaint = now;
                        dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('wixFirstPaint'));
                    });
                    observer.disconnect();
                    return true;
                }
            });
        }).observe(document.body);
    }
</script>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="text-align:center; font-size:18px;">Cheque*</p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="text-align:center; font-size:18px;"><span class="wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text"></span></p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="text-align:center; font-size:18px;">*Please make cheques payable to LSBC</p></div></div></div></div><div id="comp-k0hlc7op" class="SxM0TO QxJLC3 comp-k0hlc7op wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="text-align:center; font-size:18px;">BEFORE GIVING:</p></div><div id="comp-k0hlc7ra" class="SxM0TO QxJLC3 comp-k0hlc7ra wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="text-align:center; font-size:18px;">Please ensure that the items being donated are still in good working condition. Avoid giving items that are soiled or may not be working well. Let's bless&nbsp;others the way we wish to be blessed by&nbsp;others!</p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="text-align:center; font-size:18px;"><span class="wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text"></span></p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="text-align:center; font-size:18px;">Additionally, please contact <a href="mailto:missions@lsbc.org.sg?subject=Donations" target="_self" class="wixui-rich-text__text"></a><a data-auto-recognition="true" href="mailto:missions@lsbc.org.sg" class="wixui-rich-text__text">missions@lsbc.org.sg</a> to arrange for a suitable time and location for your items to be received by our missions team.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><div id="comp-k0hlc7xw" class="Vd6aQZ ignore-focus comp-k0hlc7xw" tabindex="-1" role="region" aria-label="Giving"><span class="mHZSwn">Giving</span></div></div></div></section><section id="comp-lng4c1wf1" tabindex="-1" class="Oqnisf comp-lng4c1wf1 wixui-section" <p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="text-align:center; font-size:18px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Joining us our next trip</span></p>
